text: Best DC in Singapore.  Very clean even on corner,  even the pantry.

I personally don't like this DC because of multiple reason.

Miles away from City
❌ 24*7 Restaurant
❌ Nearby supermarket
❌ Shopping Malls
Hard to get private taxi

About the facility provided by Equinix i would say it's one of the oldest DC with old premises. Sometimes you don't even get coffee cups in pantry.

Pretty secure facility that only allows authorised access with prior arrangements only. Have a resting area towards the right, after passing thru the 1st security area. You could simply wait there if you're waiting for your deliveries to arrive.
We consider this DC, the BEST in Singapore. Everything you need for is there.  Equinix should be a model for all DC in Singapore.
